room_title: Escape room "Spaceship Mysteries" by Time Escape in Seattle
review: Such a fun experience! We loved the whole set up, the creative puzzle, and the staff is super fun and helpful. Great way to spend 50 minutes!

room_title: Escape room "Spaceship Mysteries" by Time Escape in Seattle
review: This place is amazing! Great staff, small private room if you are doing a team builder and super cool rooms.  Everyone had a great time! Good price also, for the experience and the group size! Highly recommend!!!!

room_title: Escape room "Spaceship Mysteries" by Time Escape in Seattle
review: Loved the first escape room we've played! I've tried different escape rooms in Seattle, NYC and Toronto and this was definitely my favorite. Excited to try the other rooms that they have.
